<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الأصمعيّ:</span> هَذَأْتُ الشيء هَذْأً: قطعْتُهُ.<span class="c5"> وتَهَذَّأَتِ القَرحَةُ:</span> فسدتْ وتقطَّعتْ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>